#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.218"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.218:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.218:0.2"
msgid "22. Akkosakavagga"
msgstr "22. Abuse"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.218:0.3"
msgid "218. Dutiyaapāsādikasutta"
msgstr "218. Uninspiring Conduct (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.256"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.218:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā apāsādike."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of uninspiring conduct."

msgctxt "an5.218:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: akataṃ → na kataṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an5.218:1.3"
msgid ""
"Appasannā nappasīdanti, pasannānañca ekaccānaṃ aññathattaṃ hoti, "
"satthusāsanaṃ akataṃ hoti, pacchimā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati, "
"cittamassa nappasīdati."
msgstr ""
"You don’t inspire confidence in those without it. You cause some with "
"confidence to change their minds. You don’t follow the Teacher’s "
"instructions. Those who come after you follow your example. And your mind "
"doesn’t become clear."

msgctxt "an5.218:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā apāsādike."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of uninspiring conduct."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.218:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā pāsādike."
msgstr "There are these five benefits of inspiring conduct."

msgctxt "an5.218:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.218:2.3"
msgid ""
"Appasannā pasīdanti, pasannānañca bhiyyobhāvo hoti, satthusāsanaṃ kataṃ "
"hoti, pacchimā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati, cittamassa pasīdati."
msgstr ""
"You inspire confidence in those without it. You increase confidence in those "
"who have it. You follow the Teacher’s instructions. Those who come after you "
"follow your example. And your mind becomes clear."

msgctxt "an5.218:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā pāsādike”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits of inspiring conduct.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.218:2.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
